Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:06.75,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I am Indy Jaws
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:08.75,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,An expert on adventures!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:11.29,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I am a Great Great Great Adventurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:14.88,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,In order to change my human little sister back into a yo-kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.88,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I'm searching for the treasure yo-kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:28.99,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:32.00,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,We just got eatten!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:35.85,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:38.27,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Everything started 12 hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:41.98,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have imagined that this would happen then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:45.50,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have expected anything like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:50.65,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Busters Treasure Chapter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:53.23,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,12 hours ago
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:57.53,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,In my professional opinion, as a Great Great Great Adventurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:59.34,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,The next place we should look...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:00.57,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Is right over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:02.00,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:05.36,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,To reach this treasure, we need {\i1}his{\i0} help this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:08.83,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,We need his cooperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:11.87,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,We need
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:13.31,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,His
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:14.76,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Cooperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.83,0:01:19.50,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Mr. Scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:20.96,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.96,0:01:26.52,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,You should already know that I go on air adventures, not real ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:29.04,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Watching adventures in movies is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.18,0:01:30.08,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:32.35,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Err... I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:37.23,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I'd love to go, however I have a shop to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:39.23,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Take care. Adieu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:43.36,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,But if you come with us, you can dig as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:46.88,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:50.88,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,The place that we're headed is Saba Saba Desert, Ari Ari Ari Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:55.04,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,This treasure seems to be buried quite deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:55.85,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:59.00,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,We need someone like you, Mr.Scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:01.05,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.06,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Let's dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:04.88,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Dig dig dig with all your might!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:07.76,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Why do you like digging so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.28,0:02:12.46,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:15.10,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to dig there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:18.67,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,If you keep digging at that topic...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:22.81,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,...You're never going to come back the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:26.00,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That seems like a pretty scary episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.36,0:02:31.23,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Well... the statute of limitations passed, so I'll talk if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:32.99,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Statute of limitations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:35.29,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,This smells like a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:38.59,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It all happened under here, about five years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.32,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:42.80,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,This smells like a real serious crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:45.26,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Do you want to dig deeper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:47.18,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Ok, let's stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:48.35,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Please forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:51.28,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Ok! So are we settled?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.24,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:02.06,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,So this is Ari Ari Ari Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.80,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,So treasure is waiting right below us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:06.88,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Let's dig now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.39,0:03:09.47,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:11.58,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to get yourselves killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.39,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,If you dig here carelessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:16.49,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,You'll get swallowed by the sand, and never come out alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:23.32,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's like if you're going out with your girlfriend to the beach and burying each other to the neck with sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:26.36,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That explanation was way too long, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:30.27,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,As expected of the Great Great Great Adventurer Indy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:34.94,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Good! No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:36.14,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:41.85,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Oh my shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:45.87,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Treasure Link!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.72,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Leave the digging to me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:52.94,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What is with that shovel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:55.63,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's attached to a Yo-kai Pod!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:00.04,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Let's start digging!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:03.64,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,dig dig dig...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:07.24,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Mr.Scoop is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.60,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Dig dig dig...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.20,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's follow after!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:24.88,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Dig dig dig...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:26.33,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Wait Mr. Scoop! We've gone too far! Stop right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.38,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Dig dig... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:30.54,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:32.65,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,...trying to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.34,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,P-Please go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.61,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Please dig as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:40.62,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:44.04,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Dig dig dig...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:46.80,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Mr.Scoop's personality changes that much when they've stopped digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.77,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That's an understatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:52.33,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Bringing Mr.Scoop along might have been a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.59,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Dig dig dig...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:57.71,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.32,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's snakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:10.14,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr.Scoop. Be more careful while digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.47,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:16.03,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Dig dig dig...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:18.62,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem like Mr.Scoop is doing anything differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:21.95,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Why does Mr.Scoop lose their sense of direction while digging?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:22.83,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.05,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:26.76,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,...want to dig that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.72,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,We don't! We don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.24,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,We'll just leave the digging to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:33.77,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:36.38,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Dig dig dig...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:37.96,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:39.93,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.92,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What's with that arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:49.00,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,We should dig that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.85,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Wait! That's clearly a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:55.98,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Dig dig dig...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.93,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't dig any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.55,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Dig dig dig...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.60,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's a secret passageway!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.47,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's another arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.23,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,This way huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:11.74,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Hey wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.84,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.47,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:19.66,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,You're going to get caught in this obvious trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:26.62,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:33.63,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:37.00,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,We just got eatten!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:57.15,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Somehow, we escaped inside its eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:59.47,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That was a great adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:01.55,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I want to do that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:04.17,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,As you wish. Let's dig once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.59,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Oh... Let's not dig anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:08.68,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:10.11,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,...trying to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:14.01,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:21.83,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Yo-kai are all around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.59,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,You can't see them but,...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:28.74,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,They might even be causing trouble around you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:30.95,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,For example,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:34.37,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,When you get so tired, you fall dead asleep and can't even wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.92,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,This happen sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:40.02,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Everything is caused by yo-kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.03,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Let's use the Yo-kai Watch now....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:46.72,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,...and try to find those troublesome yo-kai.
