Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:43.75,red_romanji_lyrics,,0,0,0,,juubun wakatteta hazu darou
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:43.75,red_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,I thought I had it all figured out perfectly this time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:47.67,red_romanji_lyrics,,0,0,0,,nanoni mata kurikaesu no ne
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:47.67,red_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,But even so, the pattern repeats itself again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.26,red_romanji_lyrics,,0,0,0,,nodo mo tosugide atsusa wasure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.26,red_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,Danger past and it’s forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:56.06,red_romanji_lyrics,,0,0,0,,meguru mekuru yo jinsei gekijou
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:56.06,red_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,And so the stage show that is life plays over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.56,red_romanji_lyrics,,0,0,0,,yo no naka namecha ikenaiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.56,red_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,You can't be naïve about the world we live in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:03.40,red_romanji_lyrics,,0,0,0,,kin kira kin wa mitame dake
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:03.40,red_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,Some things only appear to be glittering like gold on the outside
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:07.07,red_romanji_lyrics,,0,0,0,,nakami ga kirai to hikatte hoshii
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:07.07,red_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,You want the inside to be shining and sparkling too
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:11.53,red_romanji_lyrics,,0,0,0,,sariganaku sariganaku aa sariganaku
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:11.53,red_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,You’re casually, casually, aah, casually hoping
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:17.00,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\pos(393,580)}The Tengu's Fierce Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:17.68,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing we went hiking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.02,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,The air is so fresh, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:28.86,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Geez
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:32.59,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:35.36,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Hey... Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.92,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.22,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Hey guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.92,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,There they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:46.12,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That wind just now was suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.72,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's got to be the work of a yo-kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.44,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:54.97,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's natural for the wind to blow that way on a mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:57.92,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,For you to put that kind of blame on a yo-kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:09:59.77,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,See? It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:00.60,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:02.60,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What yo-kai is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:06.00,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Oh! Of course I know that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:06.72,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That has got to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:08.28,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,...A handsome yo-kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:10.59,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,...a blue-faced yo-kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.01,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,...something of that sort...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:14.19,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:17.44,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,This is the yo-kai Karasu-tengu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:25.74,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\pos(258,390)}Karasutengu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:25.37,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,A legendary classic yo-kai who controls the wind and flies in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:28.03,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Oh Karasutengu-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:32.32,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Whisper, you're always looking up to classic yo-kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:35.56,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, don't tengu usually have long noses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:37.61,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Karasutengu's nose is not long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.08,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.45,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:47.58,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I was thinking that even if you were a tengu, you don't have a long nose like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.61,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Please stop with the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:02.16,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.83,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,All we said was that you didn't have a big nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:12.67,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're insecure about your nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:15.05,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,How could you say that to me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:15.92,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.39,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:21.26,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Tengu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.01,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:25.05,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I am the a true tengu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.82,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,My long nose is the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:33.02,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,A tengu doesn't need a long nose to be a tengu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.48,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,In that case, have a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:39.24,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,After surveying six million of the nation's children...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:43.39,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,"The most memorable part of a tengu" is overwhelmingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:45.84,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,The long nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:48.33,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Well, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.61,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:51.47,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Karasutengu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:57.07,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,The long nose is the proof of a true tengu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.67,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:01.55,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Why are you so fussy about the nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.34,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:10.94,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:11.88,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:13.88,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I'm Karasutengu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.85,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,But your nose isn't long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:19.39,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Your nose is seriously not very long
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:22.35,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That's super funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.99,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Nose... nose... nose...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:36.99,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Everyone else fusses over the nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.96,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Why do they acknowledge the long nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:41.96,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,But they never acknowledge me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:47.40,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Let's decide whether you're a tengu with a tengu battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:49.16,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Tengu battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.88,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:55.95,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That is how tengu settle matters ever since long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:13:00.89,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you don't seem to remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.19,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Eh? Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.62,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Of course we remember, right Jibanyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:06.32,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,You're Nekuramatengu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:08.32,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:11.36,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I live right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:12.72,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.92,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I came over to referee the tengu battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.20,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Referee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:22.19,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Every time these two have a quarrel, I come over to referee them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.48,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,They have quarrels that often?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.04,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Alright. Let's get this started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:35.04,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,This time, whoever loses this battle leaves this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:35.87,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:38.33,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I say the exact same thing back to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:42.36,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Whoa. This looks kind of serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:44.04,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,This battle has three matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:48.22,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,This first match will decide who can fly the fastest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:53.36,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,The fastest one will bring back the fan on the summit of that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:56.28,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Take your places... Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:56.92,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:00.70,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I don't intend to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.41,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:03.87,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,They're both so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.94,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Here's the result of the first match...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:18.24,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Karasutengu got ten points. Tengu got zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:21.26,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:24.72,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,The second match is a wind battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:27.28,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Who can cause the biggest winds?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.28,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.75,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Ready? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.05,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Keita's completely naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:53.05,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.29,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Here's the result of the second match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:58.36,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Karasutengu gets zero points. Tengu gets ten points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:14:59.74,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's a tie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:02.30,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's not time to get excited. Hurry up and wear your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.21,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Third match
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.72,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Geta sandals are important for a tengu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:10.59,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Whoever can kick them off the furthest is the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:12.32,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Geta kicking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.92,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I wonder what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:17.37,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,The winner of this match will get a hundred points.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:22.06,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,In other words, whoever wins the third match is the winner of this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:25.77,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,So the first and second matches basically have no meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:32.24,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,You haven't forgotten the promise that the loser leaves this mountain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.58,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I was going to say the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:37.21,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Well! Then let's begin the final match!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:40.40,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Alright! Get ready! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:46.03,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.06,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,H-H-How could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:06.03,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,The one who kicked it out the furthest is Nekuramatengu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.84,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Umm... In other words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:10.43,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That means that Nekuramatengu won the battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:13.61,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Seems like Nekuramatengu was the dark horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.40,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:27.93,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Who could have predicted such an outcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.28,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.68,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Nekuramatengu, you can do it when you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:35.60,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I would lose to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:38.16,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,But a deal is a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.01,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Here's a reward for helping with the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.21,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.42,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:52.60,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Nobody could have predicted that I would win but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:56.16,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,But for me to win a tengu battle like this...heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:17:00.06,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have seen this coming either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:03.45,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Something Watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:09.12,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\pos(332,577)}Yo-kai Batan Q
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.10,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.02,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Welcome home -nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:11.02,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.67,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Conk out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.76,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Keita, you're already asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:22.46,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,He was up late last night reading comics so he's conking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:24.46,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What does it mean to conk out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:28.40,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,To fall asleep like this. Conk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:31.48,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,To fall asleep like this means to conk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:35.31,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,By the way, the sound that I make when I conk out is "sponpee"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.76,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:41.77,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:45.93,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:50.48,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That yo-kai! Of course I know what that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:53.84,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's got a ring on it so it must be Ringy or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.96,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it's Big Beany, like a broad bean!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:57.95,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.08,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That's the yo-kai Batan Q!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.64,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,You were completely wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.64,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Let's conk out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:11.55,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\pos(253,413)}Batan Q
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:12.57,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,A yo-kai who cause people who come back home to collapse on their beds and conk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:16.27,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,A legendary yo-kai that tired people can be thankful for!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.25,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,A legendary yo-kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.45,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That's correct
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.97,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,So it was you who caused Keita to conk out just now right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:25.23,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,He seemed pretty tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:27.68,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That's why I used my soutimate move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:28.86,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Soultimate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:30.80,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Yep. Its name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:33.40,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Sanzu River Eternal Slumber
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.67,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Sanzu River Eternal Slumber?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:41.64,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Right now, Keita is having a relaxing time on Sanzu river.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.49,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:47.76,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,He was floating there the whole time that we were talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:51.45,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That's where people go to get to the afterlife, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:54.65,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Hey! Putting him there was a terrible idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:57.55,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,As long as he doesn't make it to the other side, he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:00.78,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,How is someone supposed to relax in a place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:03.04,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,If you're so worried, then take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.50,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Can we see through that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:07.50,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Let's Batan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.37,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,So this is Sanzu River
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:18.49,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,So nice
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:23.42,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Oh man. Reading comics late last at night really tired me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:27.12,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,We went on hike so long that our knees ached.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:28.52,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Komajiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:31.07,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That's right. We got a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:34.38,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I was also busying with the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:35.61,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Company?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:40.41,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's really nice to relax in outdoor places like this sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.05,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.50,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,This is such a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.50,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's like our own secret resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.46,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Our towels!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:01.45,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.32,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:05.02,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Don't cross over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:07.32,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,You're going to cross into the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:11.52,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.63,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Oh I thought I was gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:19.52,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Oh Keita! That was too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:24.28,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I've a bad feeling one of them actually crossed over though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:26.06,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,It's just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:29.71,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Oh this feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:31.71,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Floaty floaty
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:33.71,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Such relaxation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:36.65,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,This warms my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:39.37,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I want to be here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:41.76,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Keita and others are floating to the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.58,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What!? You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:46.65,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Keita! Go back! Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:49.39,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Keita! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:51.76,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.76,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:55.10,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Huh? Whisper?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:56.81,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Jibanyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:59.21,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Huh? We're getting carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:00.30,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:02.16,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,We need to swim back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:09.39,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I wasn't doing anything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:14.25,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Keita! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.25,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.54,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:24.57,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,We were pretty close to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:27.72,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Keita made it out okay somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:30.01,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired from all that yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.17,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Would you like to try going there as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:34.80,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the Sanzu River! Q!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:42.70,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:44.70,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Whisper? Jibanyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.82,0:21:53.47,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:55.47,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,A river? Don't tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:59.34,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,This is the Sanzu River.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:04.88,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,We're about to reach the other side now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:11.60,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Wait wait wait!
