Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.52,0:23:16.24,blue_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,Before the white season arrives, we’ll reminisce about summer memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:20.70,blue_romanji_lyrics,,0,0,0,,jakkurrantan minna wo terashi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:20.70,blue_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,Everyone will light their Jack-o-Lanterns
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.70,0:23:25.17,blue_romanji_lyrics,,0,0,0,,kurisumasu made mainichi paatii
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.70,0:23:25.17,blue_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,Every day until Christmas will be a party
