Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:29.96,blue_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,So come on, let’s dance, let’s keep on dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:32.13,blue_romanji_lyrics,,0,0,0,,harokuri harokuri harokuri harokuri
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:32.13,blue_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,Hello Christmas, hello Christmas, hello Christmas, hello Christmas
