Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:34.38,blue_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,Dancing and dancing to welcome Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:38.76,blue_romanji_lyrics,,0,0,0,,nennai ippai nennai ippai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:38.76,blue_lyrics_translation,,0,0,0,,Lots and lots to do before the end of the year
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.32,0:23:42.41,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Today's yo-kai medallium...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:45.10,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Keita! What's today's yo-kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:47.63,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Karasutengu and Batan Q!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:49.92,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Ahh I'm so tired
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.25,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,I'm going home and conking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.25,0:23:54.32,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Make sure you wash up first...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:55.87,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.44,0:23:59.77,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,You're conking out right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:02.41,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,On the next Yo-kai Watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:03.76,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Yo-kai Bon Odori Dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.84,0:24:09.82,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,At this time of year just as humans do, we yo-kai also have a huge summer festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.82,0:24:13.16,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Looks like a human girl got lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.16,0:24:14.25,LargeYWNH,,0,0,0,,What!?
